\c 45
\s Rwiyo pamutambo waMambo Mukuru
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba; paShoshanimi. \add Pisarema\add* revanakomana vaKora. Masikiri. Rwiyo rwerudo ruzhinji.
\p
\v 1 Moyo wangu unotutuma nyaya yakanaka; ndinotaura zvinhu zvandakaitira mambo; rurimi rwangu ipeni\x + Job. 19.24. Jer. 8.8. 17.1.\x* yemunyori anokurumidza\x + Ezi. 7.6.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Imwi makanaka kupfuura vana vevanhu; nyasha yakadururirwa pamiromo yenyu; naizvozvo Mwari wakakuropafadzai nekusingaperi\x + Ruk. 4.22.\x*.
\v 3 Sungai munondo wenyu\x + Zvak. 1.16.\x* pachidya\x + Eki. 32.27.\x*, Wemasimba\x + Isa. 9.6.\x*, ukuru hwenyu neumambo hwenyu\x + Map. 21.5.\x*.
\v 4 Ne\add mu\add*umambo hwenyu, tasvai mubudirire, nekuda kwechokwadi neunyoro \add ne\add*kururama\x + Zvak. 6.2.\x*; neruoko rwenyu rwerudyi rwukudzidzisei zvinhu zvinotyisa\x + Map. 65.5.\x*.
\v 5 Miseve yenyu inopinza pamoyo yevavengi vamambo; marudzi achawa pasi penyu\x + Map. 120.4. Zvir. 25.18. Isa. 5.28.\x*.
\v 6 Chigaro chenyu cheushe, Mwari, chiripo nekusingaperi-peri; tsvimbo yeushe hwenyu itsvimbo yekururama\x + Map. 93.2. VaHeb. 1.8,9. Map. 110.2. Zvir. 8.22.\x*.
\v 7 Munoda kururama, uye munovenga kuipa\x + Map. 11.7.\x*; naizvozvo Mwari, Mwari wenyu\x + Isa. 61.1.\x*, wakakuzodzai\x + 1 Madz. 1.39,40. Map. 2.2.\x* nemafuta emufaro kupfuura shamwari dzenyu\x + Map. 21.6.\x*.
\v 8 Nguvo dzenyu dzose imura nearosi\x + Joh. 19.39.\x* \add ne\add*akasia\x + Joh. 19.39.\x*, kubva pamizinda yenyanga dzenzou, pavakakufadzai nazvo.
\v 9 Vakunda vemadzimambo vari pakati pevanhukadzi venyu vanokudzwa\x + 45.14.\x*; vahosi vamambo\x + Neh. 2.6.\x* vamire paruoko rwerudyi rwako\x + 1 Madz. 2.19. Mat. 25.34.\x*, vakapfeka goridhe\x + Job. 28.16.\x* reOfiri\x + 1 Madz. 9.28.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Teerera, mukunda, uye ona, uye rereka nzeve yako; kanganwawo vanhu vekwako, neimba yababa vako\x + Det. 21.13.\x*.
\v 11 Ipapo mambo achashuva kunaka kwako; nokuti ndiye Ishe wako\x + Isa. 51.22.\x*; umukotamire\x + Map. 95.6. Isa. 54.5.\x*.
\v 12 Nemukunda weTire, vafumi pakati pevanhu, vachakumbira chiso chako\x + Map. 22.29. 68.29. 72.10. Isa. 49.7,23. Mat. 2.11.\x* nechipo\x + Map. 96.8. 1 Sam. 10.27.\x*.
\v 13 Mukunda wamambo anobwinya kwese\x + Job. 20.26.\x* mukati; nguvo yake ndeyemabasa akarukwa\x + Rev. 10.18. 1 Madz. 6.18.\x* egoridhe.
\v 14 Uchaperekwa kuna mambo\x + Zvak. 19.7,8.\x* akapfeka nguvo dzine mavara-mavara\x + 2 Sam. 13.18.\x*; mhandara, shamwari dzake dzinomutevera, vachaiswa kwamuri.
\v 15 Vachaperekwa nemafaro nekufarisisa; vachapinda mumuzinda wamambo.
\v 16 Panzvimbo yemadzibaba ako pachava nevana vako; achavagadza vave machinda panyika yose\x + 1 Pet. 2.9. Zvak. 1.6. 5.10. 20.6. 22.5.\x*.
\v 17 Ndicharangaridza zita renyu pamazera ese\x + Map. 10.6.\x*; naizvozvo marudzi achakurumbidzai kusvika rinhi narinhi.